<item>
            <title>[SPARK-34251] TRUNCATE TABLE resets stats for non-empty v1 table</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-34251</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The example below portraits the issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-sql&quot;&gt;
spark-&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;sql&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; tbl (c0 &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, part &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;) PARTITIONED &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; (part);
spark-&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;sql&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; tbl &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;PARTITION&lt;/span&gt; (part=0) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; 0;
spark-&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;sql&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; tbl &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;PARTITION&lt;/span&gt; (part=1) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; 1;
spark-&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;sql&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;ANALYZE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; tbl &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;COMPUTE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;STATISTICS&lt;/span&gt;;
spark-&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;sql&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;DESCRIBE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; EXTENDED tbl;
...
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;Statistics&lt;/span&gt;	4 bytes, 2 &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;rows&lt;/span&gt;
...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&apos;s truncate one partition:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-sql&quot;&gt;
spark-&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;sql&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TRUNCATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; tbl &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;PARTITION&lt;/span&gt; (part=1);
spark-&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;sql&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;DESCRIBE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; EXTENDED tbl;
...
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;Statistics&lt;/span&gt;	0 bytes, 0 &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;rows&lt;/span&gt;
...
spark-&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;sql&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; * &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; tbl;
0	0
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*The last query returns a row but stats show 0 rows. *&lt;/p&gt;</description>
